29
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:30,240
Smarty Bean?

30
00:02:30,240 --> 00:02:30,760
Yes.

31
00:02:31,640 --> 00:02:33,079
That's a pretty good name.

32
00:02:33,079 --> 00:02:33,880
Right?

33
