75
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:11,240
I took photos of everything.

76
00:04:11,240 --> 00:04:12,040
It's all here.

77
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:19,490
All these years,

78
00:04:20,600 --> 00:04:22,600
