100
00:05:25,680 --> 00:05:27,520
Whoo.

101
00:05:27,520 --> 00:05:30,000
Clickety-clack.

102
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:32,240
I was right behind that train,

103
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:33,840
