109
00:05:40,560 --> 00:05:42,040
When will it ever stop?

110
00:05:42,360 --> 00:05:43,880
I chased until I woke up.

111
00:05:43,880 --> 00:05:45,360
I got dressed and went out.

112
00:05:45,640 --> 00:05:47,680
I'm out on the streets of Shanghai.

113
00:05:47,680 --> 00:05:49,440
